      ** New Deal in Screen Format
     D NwDlScnFmt    E DS                  EXTNAME(ABFUNDPD)
     D                                     Prefix(DD:2)
 
      ** Internal funding deals error indicator file
     D OkFlags       E DS                  EXTNAME(ABEFUNDPD)
 
