     C                   PARM                    NwDlScnFmt
 
      ** Deal Currency Decimal Place
     C                   PARM                    PDecPlace
 
      ** Standing Data
      ** =============
      ** SDDEAL: Decimal Separator
     C                   PARM                    BNDCSP
 
